<p style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:left; line-height:115%;" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; "><b>用{
}圈起来的部分看似象PHP的脚本,但是有2处语法错误.</b></span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:7.5pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0cm; line-height:115%; tab-stops:list 36.0pt;" align="left"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; ">·<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; ">MzYwd2Vic2Nhbg</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; ">没有被引用</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; "></span></b></p>
<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm; margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:7.5pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0cm; line-height:115%; tab-stops:list 36.0pt;" align="left"><b><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol; ">·<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; ">}</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; ">的前面没有分号</span></b></p>
<p style="text-align:left;line-height:115%; " align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; "><b>
</b></span></p>
<p style="text-align:left;line-height:115%; " align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; "><b>其中, 有关MzYwd2Vic2Nhbg的调用由于@print的报错而被中止，如果将其用base64进行解码,就成为了360webscan.所以,这种攻击就被暂时命名为<a target="_blank" href="http://blog.tokumaru.org/2013/06/360webscan-attack.html  "><u>[360webscan攻击]</u></a>.<br>
</b></span></p>
